OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry with bright or
OL,6,Foccasional sunny spells, especially in
OL,7,Fthe east during the morning. Becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly cloudy from the west into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon, with perhaps some
OL,10,Fpatchy rain reaching the Derbyshire
OL,11,Fhills by evening. A breezier day. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA band of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes, especially over western hills,
OL,15,Fwill quickly move eastwards across all
OL,16,Fparts overnight, clearing by the early
OL,17,Fhours. Becoming drier with clearer
OL,18,Fspells. Windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
